            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Supero <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXII Exsupe<lb break="no" n="2"/>rat<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XVIII <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Vitalis et <expan><abbr>Ulp</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Cavva genero et <lb n="5"/>filiae <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>arentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Aus mehreren Fragmenten zusammengesetzt. Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Relief mit frontal gezeigten Sitzfiguren einer Frau und eines Mannes; im Relief teilweise Farbreste erhalten.</p>
            </div>
